title: Coheed & Cambria
description:
The very best Coheed & Cambria collection ever composed.

The Second Stage Turbine Blade
In Keeping Secrets Of Silent Earth: 3

plus!!

plus plus!!
There&#039;s the String Quartet Tribute To Coheed & Cambria&#039;s: In Keeping Secrets Of Silent Earth


plus plus plus!!!

Included are all 3 albums from Coheed & Cambria before they were Coheed & Cambria. When they were known as a little band by the name of Shabutie (you may know this name from the begining of their Co&Ca song "Devil In Jersey City"). Their Shabutie albums are:

Delirium Trigger EP
Plan To Take Over The World
The Penelope EP

plus there&#039;s a bunch of other non-album tracks from Shabutie:

Like I said, this is without doubt the ultimately best Co&Ca torrent ever!
